8713 - Surveying Services Summary > MCKENZIE GROUP CONSULTING PTY. LTD. is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover surveying services. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. MCKENZIE GROUP CONSULTING PTY. LTD. is headquartered in Melbourne, Victoria. It is headed by director Stephen John Natilli. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $31.43 million. Its net profit totalled $3.08 million. MCKENZIE GROUP CONSULTING PTY. LTD. forms part of the services industry sector.
